      • forType

        public static ClassOrInterfaceBound forType(java.lang.reflect.Type type)
        Create a ParameterBound for the given java.lang.reflect.Type that is defined as a class or interface. If the type is a java.lang.reflect.ParameterizedType with a type variable, then bound may be recursive, and so returns a GenericTypeBound. Otherwise, returns a ClassOrInterfaceTypeBound.
        Parameters:
        type - the Type bound
        Returns:
        a ClassOrInterfaceBound for the given type
